22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcd-rates-savings-rates-today-wednesday-12-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi's%20New%20BJP%20Government%20Starts%20Withdrawing%20Cases%20Against%20Lt%20Governor%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESignalling%20an%20end%20to%20legal%20disputes%20between%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20new%20BJP-led%20dispensation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20has%20begun%20withdrawing%20several%20court%20cases%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20cases%20are%20related%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission%20(DERC)%20chairman%2C%20funding%20for%20the%20Delhi%20Jal%20Board%2C%20appointment%20of%20lawyers%20in%20Delhi%20riots%20cases%2C%20teacher%20training%20in%20foreign%20countries%20and%20the%20high-level%20committee%20on%20Yamuna%20pollution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20AAP%20was%20in%20power%2C%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governors%20-%20Najeeb%20Jung%2C%20Anil%20Baijal%20and%20VK%20Saxena%20-%20frequently%20clashed%20over%20one%20issue%20or%20the%20other%20and%20several%20of%20these%20disagreements%20made%20their%20way%20to%20the%20courts.%20The%20AAP%20government%2C%20led%20by%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20then%20Aatishi%2C%20complained%20that%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20(LG)%20was%20deliberately%20hampering%20the%20implementation%20of%20its%20policies.%20The%20LG%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20accused%20the%20AAP%20of%20not%20cooperating%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tussle%20with%20the%20LG%20is%20seen%20as%20one%20of%20the%20factors%20that%20led%20to%20the%20AAP's%20rout%20in%20last%20month's%20Delhi%20elections.%20The%20Arvind%20Kejriwal-led%20party%20was%20reduced%20to%20just%2022%20seats%20in%20the%2070-member%20Assembly%20with%20the%20BJP%20winning%2048%20and%20returning%20to%20power%20in%20Delhi%20after%20a%20gap%20of%20more%20than%20a%20quarter%20of%20a%20century.%C2%A0The%20BJP%20government%20is%20now%20led%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20Rekha%20Gupta.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20the%20LG%20were%20at%20loggerheads%20over%20the%20appointment%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Electricity%20Regulatory%20Commission%20chairman%20because%20the%20party%20believed%20that%20letting%20the%20Centre%20control%20the%20body%20could%20lead%20to%20the%20power%20subsidy%20scheme%20-%20which%20was%20very%20popular%20among%20voters%20-%20being%20ended.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%2C%20then%20LG%20Anil%20Baijal%20was%20accused%20by%20the%20AAP%20of%20interfering%20in%20the%20appointment%20of%20public%20prosecutors%20to%20argue%20cases%20linked%20to%20the%20Northeast-Delhi%20riot%20cases.%20%26quot%3BThe%20LG%20and%20Central%20government%20are%20insisting%20on%20the%20appointment%20of%20a%20panel%20of%20special%20public%20prosecutors%20chosen%20by%20the%20Centre.%20This%20is%20happening%20at%20a%20time%20when%20there%20are%20very%20serious%20allegations%20over%20the%20response%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20to%20these%20riots%20as%20well%20as%20how%20the%20investigation%20is%20going%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20AAP%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%20had%20said%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20had%20also%20moved%20court%20over%20the%20LG%20applying%20riders%20while%20approving%20its%20proposal%20to%20send%20teachers%20to%20Finland%20for%20training.%20Senior%20advocate%20AM%20Singhvi%2C%20appearing%20for%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20had%20told%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202023%3A%20%26quot%3BLG%20is%20deciding%20which%20teachers%20to%20send%2C%20how%20to%20send%20and%20when%20to%20send.%20This%20is%20concerning%20the%20teachers'%20training%20programme.%26quot%3B%20The%20counsel%20for%20LG%20Saxena%20had%20responded%20that%20the%20Kejriwal%20government%20had%20refused%20to%20bring%20on%20record%20the%20%26quot%3Bimpact%20assessment%20of%20the%20foreign%20training%20programmes%20conducted%20in%20the%20past%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20in%20the%20Delhi%20government%20said%20that%20these%20and%20other%20cases%20will%20be%20withdrawn%20to%20resolve%20the%20confrontation%20between%20the%20dispensation%20in%20Delhi%20and%20the%20LG%20Office%20as%20well%20as%20the%20central%20government.%20%26quot%3BGovernance%20will%20get%20priority%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741774980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2F1d52ii4o_rekha-gupta_625x300_20_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-new-bjp-government-starts-withdrawing-cases-against-lt-governor-sources-7907182%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Signalling%20an%20end%20to%20legal%20disputes%20between%20the%20Lieutenant%20Governor%2C%20who%20represents%20the%20Centre%2C%20and%20the%20Delhi%20government%2C%20the%20new%20BJP-led%20dispensation%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20has%20begun%20withdrawing%20several%20court%20cases%2C%20sources%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdelhis-new-bjp-government-starts-withdrawing-cases-against-lt-governor-sources-7907182%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22World%20No.1%20Shubman%20Gill%20crowned%20ICC%20Player%20of%20the%20Month%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741774928000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118931285%2Cimgsize-48716.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fshubman-gill-crowned-icc-player-of-the-month-for-february-2025%2Farticleshow%2F118931198.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Shubman%20Gill%20has%20been%20named%20the%20ICC%20Men%E2%80%99s%20Player%20of%20the%20Month%20for%20February%202025%20after%20impressive%20ODI%20performances%2C%20amassing%20406%20runs%20in%20