ringing%20the%20nuggets%20back%20twice%20this%20year%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20its%20host%20of%20other%20LTOs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20goal%20is%20to%20make%20crispy%20chicken%20permanent%2C%26quot%3B%20Montgomery%20told%20BI%20at%20Taco%20Bell's%20Live%20M%C3%A1s%20Live%20event%20in%20March%2C%20calling%20the%20first%20release%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20experiment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMontgomery%20said%20that%20when%20the%20chain%20originally%20tested%20the%20chicken%20nuggets%20with%20consumers%2C%20%26quot%3Bit%20tested%20OK.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20launched%20it%20for%20four%20weeks%20to%20see%20how%20consumers%20responded%20to%20it%2C%20and%20we%20ran%20out%20in%20half%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20that's%20why%20we're%20bringing%20crispy%20chicken%20back%20for%2021%20weeks%20%5Bin%202025%5D.%20And%20maybe%20it's%20permanent%20in%202026.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2241d93808-4613-4c19-8b53-db81f8cdfd22%5C%22%3EChains%20know%20some%20LTOs%20aren't%20meant%20to%20last%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20fun%20of%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20too%20early%20to%20say%20whether%20the%20on-and-off%20relationship%20people%20have%20had%20with%20Taco%20Bell's%20chicken%20nuggets%20and%20Flamin'%20Hot%20Burrito%20will%20have%20a%20similar%20effect%20as%20that%20of%20the%20Mexican%20Pizza%20or%20McRib.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20chain%20executives%20are%20optimistic%20that%20LTOs%20will%20continue%20to%20drive%20brand%20excitement%20and%20engagement%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20some%20things%20that%20are%20just%20fun%20that%20we're%20not%20necessarily%20going%20to%20put%20on%20the%20menu%20full%20time%2C%20and%20we%20know%20it%20going%20in%2C%20and%20we're%20OK%20with%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Matthews%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20bring%20some%20fun%20innovation%20and%20have%20people%20get%20excited%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThink%20of%20limited-time%20offers%20as%20a%