rb%20this%20one-time%20impact.%20The%20issue%20was%20identified%20by%20the%20bank...%20The%20bank%20has%20enough%20reserves%20and%20capital%20to%20manage%20this...%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Katpalia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShares%20of%20IndusInd%20Bank%20nosedived%2027.17%20per%20cent%20to%20close%20at%20Rs%20655.95%20on%20the%20BSE.%20During%20the%20day's%20trade%2C%20the%20stock%20had%20hit%20its%201%20year%20low%20of%20Rs%20649%20a%20piece%2C%20down%2028%20per%20cent%20over%20Monday's%20closing%20price%20of%20Rs%20900.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20analyst%20call%20late%20on%20Monday%20night%2C%20Mr%20Kathpalia%20said%20that%20the%20discrepancy%20in%20the%20derivative%20portfolio%20has%20been%20accumulated%20in%20the%20book%20over%20a%20period%20of%205-7%20years%20prior%20to%20April%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20discrepancy%20in%20IndusInd%20Bank's%20treasury%20business%20went%20unnoticed%20despite%20multiple%20audits%20like%20that%20of%20internal%2C%20statutory%2C%20and%20compliance%2C%20as%20well%20as%20by%20the%20RBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20bank%20started%20reviewing%20its%20internal%20trade%20book%20after%20the%20RBI%20circular%20in%20September%202023%2C%20which%20mandated%20that%20internal%20trade%20in%20derivatives%20was%20to%20be%20discontinued%20from%20April%201%2C%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B..We%20started%20observing%20discrepancies%20in%20our%20(derivatives)%20business%20in%20October%2C%20and%20then%20we%20hired%20external%20agency%20to%20review%20our%20business.%20That%20is%20why%20we%20are%20comfortable%20that%20by%20March%20end%20or%20early%20April%2C%20we%20(external%20agency%20report)%20should%20be%20able%20to%20identify%20the%20gaps%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kathpalia%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kathpalia%20said%20that%20IndusInd%20Bank%20had%20given%20a%20%26quot%3Bpreliminary%20update%26quot%3B%20about%20this%20discrepancy%20to%20the%20banking%20regulator%20RBI%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20in%20the%20analyst%20call%20as%20to%20whether%20this%20discrepancy%20has%20had%20a%20bearing%20on%20his%20re-appointment%20as%20MD%20%26amp%3B%20CEO%2C%20Mr%20Kathpalia%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BOf%20course%20this%20would%20have%20a%20bearing%20because%20they%20were%20aware%20of%20the%20issue%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20last%20week%20approved%20only%20one%20year%20extension%20to%20Mr%20Kathpalia%20till%20March%2023%2C%202026%2C%20as%20against%20three%20years%20proposed%20by%20the%20bank's%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20know%20what's%20the%20rationale%20for%20them%20to%20give%20me%201%20year.%20But%20I%20think%20they%20are%20uncomfortable%20with%20the%20way%20my%20leadership%20skills%20of%20running%20the%20bank%20is%20and%20we%20have%20to%20respect%20that.%20This%20is%20a%20litmus%20test%20for%20the%20bank%2C%20from%20a%20succession%20point%20we%20see%20how%20to%20take%20the%20bank%20forward.%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20BAU%20(business%20as%20usual)%20of%20the%20bank%20will%20suffer%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20the%20growth%20agenda%20will%20get%20off%20the%20track%2C%26quot%3B%20Katpalia%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741772700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F1k77uah8_indusind-bank-reuters_625x300_12_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findusind-bank-hit-by-rs-2-100-crore-accounting-lapse-shares-tank-27-7900143%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22IndusInd%20Bank%20on%20Tuesday%20addressed%20the%20fallout%20of%20a%20Rs%202%2C100%20crore%20discrepancy%20in%20accounting%2C%20saying%20it%20has%20enough%20reserves%20and%20capital%20to%20cover%20for%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Findusind-bank-hit-by-rs-2-100-crore-accounting-lapse-shares-tank-27-7900143%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What's%20Making%20Once-Indifferent%20Kerala%20Finally%20Embrace%20Cricket%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20agony%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20ecstasy.%20Kerala%20lost%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20final%20against%20Vidarbha%20in%20Nagpur%E2%80%94by%20conceding%20the%20first%20innings%20lead%E2%80%94after%20having%20one%20hand%20on%20the%20cup.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20team%20would%20still%20take%20it%2C%20finishing%20second-best%20in%20India's%20premier%20First%20Class%20tournament%20out%20of%2032%20teams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala's%202024-25%20Ranji%20Trophy%20season%20was%20a%20rollercoaster%20of%20sorts.%20With%20the%20tournament%20being%20played%20in%20two%20halves%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20there%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20variables.%20It%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20three%20out%20of%20the%20seven%20league%20games%2C%20with%20two%20of%20the%20matches%20against%20Karnataka%20and%20Bengal%20getting%20washed%20out.%20The%20qualification%20was%20tricky%20and%20the%20match%20against%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20went%20down%20to%20the%20wire.%20The%20quarterfinal%20against%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20and%20the%20semifinal%20against%20Gujarat%20at%20Ahmedabad%20were%20downright%20thrillers%E2%80%94until%20it%20ran%20into%20its%20perpetual%20nemesis%20in%20Vidarbha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20had%20previously%20lost%20its%20knockout%20rounds%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20to%20Vidarbha%20in%202017-18%2C%20when%20it%20first%20made%20it%20to%20the%20quarterfinal%2C%20and%20then%20in%202018-19%2C%20when%20it%20went%20one%20step%20further%2C%20in%20the%20semifinal.%20As%20for%20Vidarbha%2C%20it%20came%20well%20prepared%2C%20having%20lost%20the%20final%20just%20as%20agonisingly%20against%20Mumbai%20last%20year.%20At%20one%20point%2C%20Kerala%20even%20looked%20poised%20to%20win.%20But%20just%20as%20skipper%20Sachin%20Baby%20was%20in%20his%20zone%2C%20accompanied%20at%20the%20crease%20by%20Jalaj%20Saxena%2C%20he%20had%20a%20brain-fade%20moment%2C%20picking%20the%20lone%20fielder%20out%20in%20the%20deep%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20a%20glory%20shot%20to%20get%20to%20his%20hundred.%20That%20put%20paid%20to%20Kerala's%20hopes%20of%20winning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1983-Moment%20for%20Kerala%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotwithstanding%20the%20near-miss%2C%20Kerala's%20run%20to%20the%20final%20this%20season%20is%20akin%20to%20India's%201983%20World%20Cup-winning%20moment.%20From%20PT%20Usha%20in%20athletics%20to%20IM%20Vijayan%20in%20football%2C%20Kerala%20has%20always%20been%20a%20sporting%20powerhouse%20that%20has%20had%20its%20share%20of%20heroes%20over%20the%20years.%20True%2C%20the%20state%20has%20produced%20national%20cricketers%20too%2C%20most%20notably%20Sanju%20Samson%2C%20in%20recent%20times.%20But%20it%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20laggard%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%2C%20with%20state%20authorities%20keen%20to%20promote%20other%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ranji%20Trophy%20itself%20has%20undergone%20tremendous%20changes%20in%20the%20past%2025%20years%2C%20including%20the%20addition%20of%20a%20number%20of%20teams.%20Kerala's%20first%20experiment%20with%20professionals%20began%20in%20the%20early%202000s%2C%20with%20former%20India%20cricketers%20Sujith%20Somasunder%20and%20Sadagopan%20Ramesh%20joining%20the%20team%20in%20different%20seasons%2C%20along%20with%20Somasetty%20Suresh.%20For%20some%20reason%2C%20Kerala%20didn't%20persist%20with%20it%2C%20until%20it%20eventually%20got%20Arun%20Karthik%2C%20Amit%20Verma%2C%20Robin%20Uthappa%20and%20Shreyas%20Gopal%20in%20recent%20times.%20With%20Aditya%20Sarwate%20and%20Baba%20Aparajith%20joining%20its%20ranks%20this%20season%2C%20Kerala%20had%20three%20professionals%20in%20the%20team%20for%20the%20first%20time%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20professionals%20is%20nothing%20to%20be%20ashamed%20of%2C%20given%20that%20Kerala%20cricketers%20in%20the%20past%2C%20such%20as%20M.%20Suresh%20Kumar%2C%20had%20played%20for%20Railways%3B%20even%20Vidarbha%20has%20two%20professionals%E2%80%94including%20Kerala-origin%20Karun%20Nair%E2%80%94playing%20for%20it%20now.%20Notably%2C%20Nair%20was%20keen%20to%20play%20for%20his%20home%20state%20after%20having%20been%20dumped%20by%20Karnataka%20on%20account%20of%20poor%20form%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20ago.%20But%20by%20the%20time%20the%20wise%20men%20at%20the%20Kerala%20Cricket%20Association%20confabulated%20and%20got%20back%20to%20him%2C%20Vidarbha%20had%20already%20struck%20a%20deal%20with%20him.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20It%20All%20Began%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala's%20participation%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20began%20in%20the%20early%201950s'%2C%20when%20it%20made%20its%20debut%20in%20the%20premier%20domestic%20competition%20as%20Travancore-Cochin%20in%201951-52%20at%20the%20initiative%20of%20GV%20Raja%2C%20an%20avid%20sports%20enthusiast.%20Ranji%20Trophy%20used%20to%20be%20a%20zonal%20knockout%20tournament%20those%20days%2C%20and%20Kerala%20was%20routinely%20defeated%20in%20the%20first%20rounds.%20Only%201953-54%20was%20an%20exception%2C%20when%20it%20made%20it%20to%20the%20second%20level.%20The%20team%20was%20led%20by%20brothers%20PM%20Raghavan%20and%20PM%20Anandan%2C%20both%20hailing%20from%20Thalassery%E2%80%94then%20part%20of%20Malabar%E2%80%94until%201957-58%2C%20when%20Travancore-Cochin%20was%20replaced%20by%20Kerala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20Raghavan%20and%20Anandan%20were%20nephews%20of%20Mambally%20Bapu%2C%20who%2C%20according%20to%20popular%20lore%2C%20baked%20the%20%E2%80%9Cfirst%20Christmas%20cake%E2%80%9D%20in%20India%20in%201883.%20The%20following%20generation%20of%20Mambally%20cricketers%20included%20PMK%20Mohandas%2C%20PMK%20Raghunath%20and%20APM%20Gopalakrishnan%2C%20all%20of%20whom%20continued%20the%20family%20tradition%20by%20establishing%20bakeries%20across%20the%20state%20after%20their%20playing%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20has%20had%20iconic%20cricketers%2C%20such%20as%20leg-spinner%20KN%20Ananthapadmanabhan%2C%20off-spinner%20B%20Ramprakash%2C%20all-rounder%20Sunil%20Oasis%20in%20the%20%E2%80%9890s%2C%20along%20with%20Sreekumar%20Nair%2C%20part%20of%20the%20India%20Under-19%20winning%20team%20in%202000.%20Things%20got%20better%20for%20the%20state's%20cricket%20at%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20millennium%20when%20Ranji%20Trophy%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20national%20league%20competition%2C%20from%20a%20zonal%20one.%20Until%20then%2C%20Kerala's%20best%20performance%20was%20making%20the%20pre-quarterfinal%20in%201994-95.%20When%20Tinu%20Yohannan%20made%20it%20to%20the%20national%20team%20in%202001%20as%20the%20first%20cricketer%20representing%20Kerala%2C%20it%20gave%20a%20fillip%20to%20the%20sport%20altogether.%20This%20was%20followed%20by%20the%20much%20more%20popular%20debut%20of%20S.%20Sreesanth%20in%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20made%20it%20to%20the%20semifinals%20of%20the%20Syed%20Mushtaq%20Ali%20Trophy%2C%20India's%20domestic%20T20%20tournament%20in%202013%2C%20on%20the%20back%20of%20some%20of%20its%20young%20stars%20getting%20exposure%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Kochi%20Tuskers%20Kerala%20team%2C%20in%20its%20lone%20season%2C%20in%202011.%20The%20Kerala%20team%20kept%20getting%20better%20and%20began%20performing%20consistently%20in%20the%20Vijay%20Hazare%20Trophy%2C%20the%20domestic%2050-over%20tournament%2C%20in%20the%20years%20that%20followed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EGrassroots%20Cricket%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20initiative%20to%20inspire%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20cricketers%2C%20the%20Kerala%20Cricket%20Association%20(KCA)%20flew%20a%20batch%20of%2045%20boys%20from%20the%20state's%20Under-14%20and%20Under-16%20teams%20to%20the%20Jamtha%20stadium%20in%20Vidarbha%20for%20the%20final.%20They%20were%20flown%20back%20in%20a%20plane%20specially%20chartered%20by%20the%20KCA%20to%20bring%20back%20Kerala's%20vanquished%20team.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala's%20recently%20launched%20T20%20league%2C%20on%20the%20lines%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20should%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20popularising%20cricket%20among%20the%20football-crazy%20people%20of%20the%20state.%20Gone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20Malayalis%20played%20gully%20cricket%20with%20improvised%20coconut%20willows.%20Cricket%20academies%20are%20springing%20up%20even%20in%20mofussil%20towns%20in%20the%20state%20today.%20Coaches%20also%20play%20an%20important%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20cricketers%2C%20and%20Amay%20Khurasiya%20has%20contributed%20tremendously%20to%20sending%20Kerala%20to%20the%20Ranji%20final%20this%20season.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20his%20big-hitting%20prowess%20in%20his%20playing%20days%2C%20Khurasiya%20gained%20prominence%20among%20Indian%20fans%20when%20he%20went%20on%20to%20get%20selected%20ahead%20of%20Vinod%20Kambli%20for%20the%201999%20World%20Cup.%20He%20was%20instrumental%20in%20instilling%20the%20virtues%20of%20grafting%20and%20a%20never-say-die%20attitude%20within%20this%20team.%20This%20season%2C%20Kerala%20reaped%20the%20rewards%20for%20its%20teamwork%20and%20was%20clearly%20more%20than%20the%20sum%20of%20its%20parts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Lies%20Ahead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECan%20Kerala%20go%20one%20step%20further%20in%20the%20Ranji%20Trophy%20next%20year%3F%20Considering%20the%20team%20was%20without%20Sanju%20Samson%20and%20Baba%20Aparajith%20for%20much%20of%20the%20season%2C%20it%20seems%20possible%20to%20improve%20its%20showing.%20However%2C%20the%20team%20clearly%20lacks%20a%20big-scoring%20top-order%20batsman%20like%20Karun%20Nair%2C%20and%20unless%20some%20of%20the%20youngsters%20step%20up%2C%20Kerala%20will%20find%20it%20tough%20to%20dominate%20the%20big%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20would%20also%20do%20well%20to%20persuade%20Sandeep%20Warrier%20to%20get%20back%20to%20the%20side%20to%20bolster%20its%20fast-bowling%20unit%20after%20the%20speedster%20switched%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%20two%20seasons%20ago.%20The%20KCA%20needs%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20widens%20its%20pool%20of%20players.%20The%20keen%20observers%20of%20the%20game%20would%20know%20that%20Kerala%20has%20pretty%20much%20had%20the%20same%20pool%20of%20around%2030%20players%20in%20the%20last%20decade.%20If%20the%20team%20can%20persuade%20the%20Kerala-born%20Devdutt%20Padikkal%20or%20Karun%20Nair%20to%20play%20for%20it%20next%20season%2C%20that%20would%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20bolstering%20its%20prospects%20and%20overcoming%20the%20heartbreak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Anand%20Kochukudy%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20and%20columnist)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741772640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Ft2bhuteo_kerala-twitter_625x300_21_February_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhats-making-kerala-finally-embrace-cricket-7907227%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20Ranji%20season%2C%20Kerala%20reaped%20the%20rewards%20for%20its%20teamwork%20and%20was%20clearly%20more%20than%20the%20sum%20of%20its%20parts.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhats-making-kerala-finally-embrace-cricket-7907227%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Militants%20hijack%20train%20after%20blowing%20up%20rail%20track%20-%20as%20security%20forces%20try%20to%20rescue%20hundreds%20of%20hostages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741772520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F25%2F03%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-pakistan-train-hijack_6854000.jpg%3F20250312111711%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-militants-hijack-train-after-blowing-up-rail-track-as-security-forces-try-to-rescue-hundreds-of-hostages-13326922%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Security%20forces%20have%20exchanged%20gunfire%20with%20separatist%20militants%20who%20have%20hijacked%20a%20train%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20as%20they%20try%20to%20free%20around%20250%20hostages%20on%20board.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fpakistan-militants-hijack-train-after-blowing-up-rail-track-as-security-forces-try-to-rescue-hundreds-of-hostages-13326922%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpakistan-militants-hijack-train-after-blowing-up-rail-track-as-security-forces-try-to-rescue-hundreds-of-hostages-13326922%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fpakistan-militants-hijack-train-after-blowing-up-rail-track-as-security-forces-try-to-rescue-hundreds-of-hostages-13326922%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3B8%20Urns%20With%20Bones%2C%20Hair%26quot%3B%3A%20A%20'Black%20Magic'%20Twist%20In%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20Fraud%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20trustees%20of%20Mumbai's%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20have%20made%20shocking%20allegations%20of%20black%20magic%20as%20the%20premier%20healthcare%20facility%20made%20headlines%20due%20to%20a%20huge%20misappropriation%20of%20funds.%20The%20current%20members%20of%20Lilavati%20Kirtilal%20Mehta%20Medical%20Trust%20have%20alleged%20that%20former%20trustees%20siphoned%20off%20funds%20to%20the%20tune%20of%201%2C200%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20alleged%20that%20black%20magic%20was%20performed%20on%20the%20hospital's%20premises%20and%20that%20they%20found%20eight%20urns%20containing%20bones%20and%20human%20hair%20under%20the%20office%20of%20the%20current%20trustees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20trust%20has%20filed%20complaints%20with%20police%20and%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20three%20FIRs%20have%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20former%20trustees.%20The%20complaints%20alleged%20that%20the%20financial%20irregularities%20have%20affected%20operations%20at%20the%20Bandra%20Hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMore%20than%20three%20FIRs%20have%20been%20filed%20against%20the%20former%20trustees%20and%20other%20related%20individuals.%20A%20fourth%20proceeding%20against%20these%20individuals%20is%20now%20pending%20before%20the%20Learned%20Magistrate%20which%20is%20based%20on%20our%20complaint%20filed%20in%20the%20Bandra%20Police%20Station%20for%20black%20magic%20and%20occult%20practices%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20trust's%20Permanent%20Resident%20Trustee%20Prashant%20Mehta%20told%20the%20media%20yesterday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20committed%20to%20upholding%20the%20integrity%20of%20the%20Lilavati%20Kirtilal%20Mehta%20Medical%20Trust%20and%20ensuring%20that%20funds%20meant%20for%20healthcare%20services%20are%20used%20solely%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20patients%20who%20rely%20on%20us%20daily.%20The%20gross%20misconduct%20and%20financial%20misappropriation%20uncovered%20during%20forensic%20audit%20is%20not%20just%20a%20betrayal%20of%20the%20trust%20placed%20in%20the%20alleged%20and%20fraudulent%20former%20trustees%2C%20but%20a%20direct%20threat%20to%20the%20very%20mission%20of%20our%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20The%20Audit%20Revealed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20trustees%20took%20control%20of%20the%20trust%20after%20a%20long%20legal%20battle.%20Chetan%20Dalal%20Investigation%20and%20Management%20Services%20and%20ADB%20and%20Associates%20conducted%20a%20forensic%20audit.%20The%20audit%20found%20large-scale%20irregularities%2C%20manipulation%20and%20siphoning%20of%20funds%20by%20the%20former%20trustees%2C%20Mr%20Mehta%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20undertook%20audits%20and%20the%20forensic%20auditors%20have%20come%20up%20with%20more%20than%20five%20reports%2C%20which%20clearly%20state%20that%20more%20than%20Rs%201%2C500%20crore%20has%20been%20siphoned%20and%20misappropriated%20by%20this%20illegal%20group%20of%20trustees.%20This%20money%20has%20been%20siphoned%20off%20by%20former%20trustees%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20NRIs%20and%20residents%20of%20Dubai%20and%20Belgium%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20allegations%20include%20illegal%20dealings%20with%20third-party%20distributors%20during%20procurements%20and%20utilising%20trust%20funds%20for%20personal%20expenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20'Black%20Magic'%20Charge%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParambir%20Singh%2C%20executive%20director%20of%20the%20hospital%20and%20Mumbai's%20former%20Police%20Commissioner%2C%20said%20the%20current%20trustees%20made%20a%20startling%20revelation%20when%20they%20took%20charge.%20%26quot%3BSome%20employees%20said%20articles%20part%20of%20black%20magic%20practices%20have%20been%20placed%20under%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20current%20trustees'%20office.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20witnesses%20and%20under%20videography%2C%20we%20dug%20up%20the%20floor%20and%20found%20eight%20urns.%20They%20had%20human%20remains%2C%20bones%2C%20hair%2C%20and%20rice%20and%20other%20items%20used%20in%20black%20magic%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20they%20approached%20the%20police%20to%20register%20a%20case%20under%20a%20Maharashtra%20law.%20When%20the%20police%20refused%2C%20they%20went%20to%20the%20court%20and%20it%20ordered%20an%20inquiry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741772460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F0htc4itg_lilavati-hospital_625x300_12_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flilavati-hospital-fraud-8-urns-with-bones-hair-a-black-magic-angle-in-lilavati-hospital-fraud-7907224%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20trustees%20of%20Mumbai's%20Lilavati%20Hospital%20have%20made%20shocking%20allegat