r%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgeoffrey-hinton-godfather-ai-nobel-prize-physics-john-hopfield-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeoffrey%20Hinton%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20has%20been%20referred%20to%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgodfather%20of%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b1cae527-2901-43d1-acce-3851f756bed0%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDaniel%20Rowland%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ERowland%20joined%20xAI%20nearly%20a%20year%20ago%20and%20oversees%20both%20of%20xAI's%20data%20centers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20organizational%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20built%20its%20Memphis%20data%20center%20%E2%80%94%20which%20Musk%20has%20said%20is%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20which%20the%20company%20has%20said%20houses%20more%20than%20200%2C000%20GPUs%20%E2%80%94%20in%20122%20days%2C%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20time%20it%20typically%20takes%20to%20build%20such%20a%20facility.%20The%20company%20also%20has%20two%20other%20facilities%20in%20Memphis%2C%20including%20a%20wastewater%20treatment%20plant%20and%20a%20site%20that%20was%20announced%20in%20March.%20Musk%20has%20said%20the%20company%20plans%20to%20scale%20the%20site%2C%20which%20he%20has%20nicknamed%20%26quot%3BColossus%2C%26quot%3B%20to%202%20million%20GPUs%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ExAI%20also%20quietly%20set%20up%20a%20data%20center%20in%20Atlanta%20in%20December%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fxai-elon-musk-x-new-atlanta-data-center-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehouses%20about%2012%2C000%20GPUs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERowland%20has%20a%20team%20of%20a%20few%20dozen%20people%2C%20including%20eight%20direct%20reports.%20In%20January%2C%20two%20of%20those%20employees%20left%20Tesla's%20Dojo%20project%2C%20which%20is%20focused%20on%20building%20the%20carmaker's%20custom%20supercomputer%2C%20to%20join%20the%20data%20center%20project%2C%20LinkedIn%20profiles%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3