%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1341%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fcaptain-of-solong-container-ship-involved-in-north-sea-crash-is-russian-national-company-says-13326888%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcaptain-of-solong-container-ship-involved-in-north-sea-crash-is-russian-national-company-says-13326888%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fcaptain-of-solong-container-ship-involved-in-north-sea-crash-is-russian-national-company-says-13326888%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opposition%20To%20Opportunity%3A%20How%20Jio%20And%20Airtel%20Finally%20Partnered%20With%20Starlink%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20development%2C%20Jio%20Platforms%20has%20announced%20a%20collaboration%20with%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20to%20offer%20Starlink%20internet%20services%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20this%20partnership%20is%20contingent%20upon%20SpaceX%20obtaining%20the%20necessary%20approvals%20from%20the%20Indian%20government%20before%20commencing%20operations%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStarlink%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20a%20way%20into%20the%20Indian%20market%20since%20October%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20to%20this%20collaboration%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20initial%20resistance%20from%20both%20Jio%20and%20Airtel%2C%20who%20opposed%20Starlink's%20entry%20into%20the%20Indian%20market.%20The%20two%20telecom%20giants%2C%20along%20with%20Starlink%2C%20were%20poised%20to%20launch%20satellite%20broadband%20services%20in%20India%20following%20the%20government's%20decision%20to%20allocate%20spectrum%20administratively.%20Jio%20had%20advocated%20for%20an%20auction-based%20approach%2C%20while%20the%20government%20preferred%20to%20follow%20global%20practices%20and%20allocate%20spectrum%20administratively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20India%20Mobile%20Congress%20(IMC)%202024%2C%20Sunil%20Mittal%2C%20the%20chairman%20of%20Bharti%20Airtel%2C%20emphasised%20the%20need%20for%20a%20level%20playing%20field%2C%20stating%20that%20satellite%20companies%20should%20be%20required%20to%20purchase%20spectrum%20and%20pay%20license%20fees%2C%20just%20like%20traditional%20telecom%20companies.%20Mittal's%20stance%20was%20echoed%20by%20Jio%2C%20which%20had%20also%20called%20for%20satellite%20firms%20to%20be%20treated%20on%20par%20with%20telecom%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20responded%20to%20Jio's%20comments%2C%20characterising%20the%20demand%20for%20an%20auction-based%20approach%20as%20%26quot%3Bunprecedented.%26quot%3B%20Following%20Mittal's%20speech%20at%20the%20IMC%2C%20Musk%20expressed%20frustration%2C%20asking%20if%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20much%20trouble%26quot%3B%20for%20Starlink%20to%20obtain%20permission%20to%20operate%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20initial%20reservations%2C%20both%20Jio%20and%20Airtel%20have%20now%20partnered%20with%20Starlink.%20Jio's%20announcement%20comes%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20Bharti%20Airtel's%20similar%20deal%20with%20SpaceX.%20This%20development%20sets%20the%20stage%20for%20intense%20competition%20between%20the%20two%20telecom%20giants%2C%20not%20only%20in%20traditional%20broadband%20but%20also%20in%20the%20satellite%20internet%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20between%20Jio%20and%20SpaceX%20enables%20the%20companies%20to%20explore%20synergies%20and%20deliver%20reliable%20broadband%20services%20across%20India%2C%20including%20rural%20and%20remote%20areas.%20Jio's%20position%20as%20the%20world's%20largest%20mobile%20operator%20in%20terms%20of%20data%20traffic%2C%20combined%20with%20Starlink's%20expertise%20in%20low%20Earth%20orbit%20satellite%20constellation%20operations%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20enhance%20the%20country's%20digital%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBharti%20Airtel's%20Managing%20Director%20and%20Vice%20Chairman%2C%20Gopal%20Vittal%2C%20hailed%20the%20partnership%20with%20SpaceX%20as%20a%20significant%20milestone%2C%20demonstrating%20the%20company's%20commitment%20to%20next-generation%20satellite%20connectivity.%20The%20agreement%20is%20expected%20to%20enable%20Airtel%20and%20SpaceX%20to%20explore%20opportunities%20for%20collaboration%20and%20expand%20their%20offerings%20in%20the%20Indian%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20agreement%20will%20enable%20Airtel%20and%20SpaceX%20to%20further%20explore%20how%20Starlink%20can%20complement%20and%20expand%20Airtel's%20offerings%2C%20and%20how%20Airtel's%20expertise%20in%20the%20Indian%20market%20could%20complement%20SpaceX's%20direct%20offerings%20to%20consumers%20and%20businesses%2C%26quot%3B%20Airtel%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20developments%20follow%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20and%20his%20meeting%20with%20Elon%20Musk.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741768260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F4bu5a2cg_jio-starlink-reuters_625x300_12_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fopposition-to-opportunity-how-jio-and-airtel-finally-partnered-with-starlink-7906691%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20journey%20to%20this%20collaboration%20has%20been%20marked%20by%20initial%20resistance%20from%20both%20Jio%20and%20Airtel%2C%20who%20opposed%20Starlink's%20entry%20into%20the%20Indian%20market.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fopposition-to-opportunity-how-jio-and-airtel-finally-partnered-with-starlink-7906691%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Are%20Your%20Mangoes%20Safe%3F%20How%20to%20Spot%20Artificially%20Ripened%20Ones%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENothing%20says%20summer%20like%20a%20juicy%2C%20sweet%20mango.%20But%20with%20reports%20of%20artificially%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%2