tion%20Policy%2C%20which%20lays%20down%20a%20three-language%20policy.%20%26quot%3BOur%20education%20minister%20said%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20excelled%20in%20PM%20SHRI%20scheme%2C%20so%20we%20are%20supposed%20to%20get%20funds.%20Why%20are%20you%20tying%20it%20up%20with%20NEP.%20He%20(Pradhan)%20said%2C%20'Tamil%20Nadu%20is%2040%20years%20behind%20and%20you%20people%20should%20wake%20up%2C%20why%20are%20u%20not%20letting%20students%20learn%20Hindi%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaiko%20said%20when%20he%20got%20the%20opportunity%20to%20speak%2C%20he%20told%20the%20minister%2C%20%26quot%3BTamil%20Nadu%20is%20not%2040%20years%20behind.%20Compared%20to%20northern%20states%2C%20we%20are%2040%20years%20ahead.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MDMK%20leader%20said%20political%20parties%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20except%20the%20BJP%2C%20have%20been%20stressing%20that%20they%20won't%20accept%20a%20three-language%20policy.%20%26quot%3BSince%20the%20NEP%20insists%20on%20a%20three-language%20formula%2C%20we%20have%20suggested%20certain%20changes.%20If%20they%20bring%20in%20the%20changes%2C%20we%20don't%20mind%20signing%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Vaiko%2C%20who%20represents%20Tiruchirapalli%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20stressed%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20parties%20are%20not%20against%20Hindi.%20%26quot%3BHindi%20Pracharak%20Sabha%20has%20been%20functioning%20in%20Chennai%20for%2060-70%20years.%20but%20we%20don't%20want%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20batted%20for%20English%20and%20said%20it%20was%20a%20means%20of%20communicating%20with%20the%20people%20and%20India%20needs%20to%20master%20it%20as%20it%20pushes%20to%20become%20the%20third%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20people%20of%20South%20(India)%2C%20English%20has%20been%20a%20means%20of%20progress.%20Tamilians%20dominate%20worldwide%2C%20across%20sectors%2C%20be%20it%20IT%20or%20medical%20science.%20They%20are%20dominating%20because%20of%20English%20proficiency%20and%20how%20did%20we%20get%20there%3A%20because%20of%20a%20two-language%20policy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20parties%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20and%20the%20Centre%20are%20locked%20in%20a%20face-off%20over%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20and%20the%20three-language%20formula.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20Education%20Minister%20Pradhan%20has%20accused%20the%20MK%20Stalin%20government%20of%20creating%20%26quot%3Bfear%20psychosis%26quot%3B%20about%20the%20three-language%20formula%20while%20doing%20little%20to%20promote%20Tamil%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minister%20said%20that%20while%20students%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%20are%20increasingly%20opting%20for%20English%2C%20the%20DMK%20government%20is%20questioning%20the%20need%20for%20a%20three-language%20formula.%20%26quot%3BNobody%20is%20imposing%20anything%20on%20anyone.%20This%20is%20a%20democratic%20society%20and%20the%20order%20of%20the%20time%20is%20you%20have%20to%20be%20multilingual%2C%26quot%3B%20Pradhan%20said.%20%26quot%3BOpposition%20to%20NEP%202020%20has%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20the%20preservation%20of%20Tamil%20pride%2C%20language%20and%20culture%20but%20everything%20to%20do%20with%20gaining%20political%20dividends.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741767480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fj5egnd3g_vaiko-mp_625x300_12_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdurai-vaiko-tamil-nadu-language-row-national-education-policy-tamil-nadu-40-years-ahead-of-north-states-mdmk-mp-on-language-row-7906611%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Amid%20the%20language%20row%20in%20Parliament%2C%20a%20Tamil%20Nadu%20MP%20has%20said%20the%20%26quot%3Bnorthern%20states%20are%2040%20years%20behind%26quot%3B%20the%20southern%20state%2C%20and%20that%20people%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%20dominate%20almost%20all%20spheres%20because%20of%20a%20two-language%20formula.%22%2C%2