20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%20accessible%20only%20by%20invitation%2C%20Manus%20has%20quickly%20gained%20traction%2C%20with%20its%20official%20Discord%20server%20growing%20to%20more%20than%20170%2C000%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20name%20comes%20from%20the%20Latin%20motto%20%26quot%3BMens%20et%20Manus%26quot%3B%2C%20meaning%20%26quot%3Bmind%20and%20hand%26quot%3B%20--%20a%20nod%20to%20its%20integration%20of%20knowledge%20and%20practical%20application.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EExclusive%20access%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManus%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsystem%20that%20can%20carry%20out%20tasks%20autonomously%20on%20behalf%20of%20users%26quot%3B%2C%20said%20Manoj%20Harjani%2C%20a%20research%20fellow%20at%20Singapore's%20S.%20Rajaratnam%20School%20of%20International%20Studies%20(RSIS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDeepSeek%20and%20ChatGPT%20differ%20from%20Manus%20in%20that%20they%20provide%20responses%20to%20prompts%20from%20users%20through%20a%20chat-style%20interface%2C%20whereas%20Manus%20is%20able%20to%20execute%20tasks%20such%20as%20booking%20tickets%20and%20sorting%20through%20resumes%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20DeepSeek%20was%20quietly%20developed%20behind%20the%20scenes%20before%20rising%20to%20prominence%2C%20Manus%20is%20taking%20a%20different%20route%20--%20limiting%20access%20to%20an%20invite-only%20beta%20and%20targeting%20enterprise-level%20clients%2C%20one%20analyst%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20this%20exclusivity%20can%20generate%20buzz%2C%20it%20may%20also%20impede%20widespread%20adoption%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Marina%20Zhang%2C%20an%20associate%20professor%20at%20the%20University%20of%20Technology%20Sydney's%20Australia-China%20Relations%20Institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20warned%20Manus%20may%20not%20cultivate%20the%20same%20broad%20appeal%20as%20DeepSeek%2C%20which%20built%20a%20large%20community%20through%20open-source%20engagement%2C%20if%20it%20continues%20to%20retain%20a%20closed%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20AFP%20tested%20Manus%20with%20an%20invitation%20code%20given%20by%20the%20company%2C%20the%20AI%20assistant%20took%20significantly%20longer%20than%20DeepSeek%20to%20generate%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20able%20to%20complete%20more%20difficult%20tasks%20compared%20to%20its%20Chinese%20rival%20or%20ChatGPT%2C%20like%20creating%20custom%20websites.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ETouchy%20topics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20while%20DeepSeek%20said%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bprogrammed%26quot%3B%20to%20provide%20answers%20that%20toe%20the%20government%20line%20on%20topics%20considered%20politically%20sensitive%20in%20China%2C%20Manus%20was%20able%20to%20give%20accurate%2C%20non-censored%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20topic%20of%20the%20bloody%201989%20crackdown%20on%20pro-democracy%20protesters%20in%20and%20around%20Tiananmen%20Square%20in%20Beijing%2C%20Manus%20responded%20by%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Chinese%20government%20carried%20out%20a%20violent%20crackdown%20on%20pro-democracy%20protesters%20in%20Tiananmen%20Square%20in%20Beijing%26quot%3B%2C%20followed%20by%20six%20more%20paragraphs%20detailing%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20gave%20a%20comprehensive%20answer%20when%20asked%20about%20allegations%20of%20human%20rights%20abuses%20by%20Beijing%20in%20Xinjiang.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20its%20uncensored%20replies%2C%20the%20programme%20said%20it%20does%20not%20%26quot%3Bintentionally%20censor%20factual%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20discussing%20sensitive%20topics%20like%20historical%20events%20or%20human%20rights%20issues%2C%20I%20aim%20to%20provide%20balanced%2C%20objective%20information%20that%20helps%20users%20understand%20complex%20subjects%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20could%20likely%20be%20because%20Manus%20%26quot%3Bis%20focused%20on%20tasks%20and%20the%20team%20didn