20yet%3F%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Megha%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jodhpur%20MBA%E2%80%99s%20Millet%20Creations%20Turn%20Into%20a%20Multi-Crore%20Bakery%2C%20Winning%20PM%E2%80%99s%20Praise%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20back%2C%20Jodhpur-based%20Amit%20Soni%20was%20tasked%20by%20the%20PUSA%20Institute%2C%20short%20for%20Indian%20Agricultural%20Research%20Institute%20(IARI)%20%E2%80%94%20to%20create%20millet-based%20confectioneries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20decided%20to%20craft%20a%20chocolate%20truffle%20cake%20using%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%20%3C%2Fem%3E(pearl%20millet)%20%E2%80%94%20a%20grain%20often%20overlooked%20due%20to%20its%20lack%20of%20gluten%20and%20distinct%20taste.%20After%20a%20month%20of%20experimenting%20and%20refining%20his%20recipe%2C%20Amit%E2%80%99s%20millet%20cake%20was%20finally%20ready!%20He%E2%80%99d%20prepared%20a%20staggering%2080%20kilograms%20of%20this%20millet%20masterpiece%2C%20divided%20into%20eight%20massive%2010-kilogram%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSome%20CAZRI%20(Central%20Arid%20Zone%20Research%20Institute)%20officials%20picked%20the%20cake.%20And%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20see%20commandoes%20along%20with%20them.%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20where%20our%20hefty%20cake%20was%20headed%20after%20they%20dispatched%20it%20to%20PUSA%20in%20Delhi%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELittle%20did%20he%20know%20that%20this%20audacious%20endeavour%20would%20catch%20the%20attention%20of%20the%20nation%E2%80%99s%20highest%20echelons.%20Two%20days%20later%2C%20he%20received%20a%20message%20with%20a%20video%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECuriosity%20piqued%2C%20he%20opened%20it%20only%20to%20witness%20a%20sight%20that%20left%20him%20astounded%20%E2%80%94%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20himself%20was%20slicing%20into%20his%20millet%20cake.%20He%20was%20flanked%20by%20dignitaries%20like%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20Kailash%20Choudhary%2C%20and%20Rajnath%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Amit%20and%20his%20brother%20Sumit%20sell%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20millet%20products%20like%20cookies%2C%20brownies%2C%20cakes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FAmit-Soni-millets-2-1741070976-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-411183%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAmit%20and%20his%20brother%20Sumit%20sell%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20millet%20products%20like%20cookies%2C%20brownies%2C%20cakes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20was%20overcome%20with%20disbelief%20and%20pride%20as%20he%20watched%20his%20creation%20being%20appreciated%20at%20such%20a%20high-profile%20event.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20nothing%20short%20of%20a%20goosebumps%20moment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvert